00:12:01,846 --> 00:12:05,249
Namamu Nadezhda,
tapi kau pakai nama Nadia.

215
00:12:05,283 --> 00:12:07,918
Aku benci Nadezhda.

216
00:12:07,953 --> 00:12:10,087
Jangan.

217
00:12:10,122 --> 00:12:13,157
Itu nama orang rusia yang indah.

218
00:12:13,192 --> 00:12:16,628
