225
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:33,977
tapi aku selalu dengarkan rekamannya

226
00:12:34,012 --> 00:12:36,480
<i>judulnya The Snow Maiden.</i>

227
00:12:36,514 --> 00:12:39,048
Mmm.

